Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G1 大獎賽 in平安京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天終於來到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭開歷史嶄新一頁的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一屆牛車大獎賽 in平安京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實況播音由我 藤原定家擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解說由宇都宮賴綱擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生 大獎賽就要開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為平安之世帶來一陣新風的最大的盛會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬眾矚目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 就介紹一下大家都很關注的路線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從朱雀院附近的起跑線出發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿朱雀大路南下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出羅城門之後向東前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一度北上跨過鴨川 向清水寺進發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有個檢修站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二度跨過鴨川北上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿一條大路西行 繼而沿大內裏左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後返回朱雀大路的這麼一條市區線路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生 你認為關鍵點在哪處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是清水寺附近的坡道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上下坡都是陡坡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要很好的控制牛的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來介紹起點的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取得發車頭位的是音速浪子 在原業平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第二發車位的是年輕的烈馬 陽成院貞明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排在第三的是技巧出眾的文屋康秀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四位的是因幡雄鷹 在原行平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五位的是牛車百戰 良岑宗貞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一位是宇治怪僧 喜撰法師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在預選中落敗的是大友黑主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.47,0:01:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 誰將登上象徵榮耀的第一代冠軍寶座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史性的一刻即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 現在是「定家之屋」時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的客人 是為平安初期添彩的三人眾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在原業平先生 小野小町小姐 文屋康秀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是被稱為六歌仙的歌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 業平先生據稱是光源氏原型的美男子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町小姐是世界三大美女之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷笑話名流康秀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你為我考量 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兩位男性和一位女性這種鐵三角組合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 沒有發生什麼三角戀之類的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,710)}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,710)}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是否定得斬釘截鐵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 業平大人的女性關係太危險了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅去招惹陛下妃子的候補 甚至對齋宮也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齋宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說從未婚的內親王之中選出來 尤為神聖的皇女齋宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛總是充滿著坎坷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏手畏腳是談不成戀愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得冠冕堂皇 你只不過是個肉食系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 而且是超級肉食系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級肉食系嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在21世紀都快成為瀕危物種了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說 是期望滅絕物種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這麼一說 小町小姐不是更應該成為你的目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照實說吧 我是那種所謂的巨乳愛好者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 人生不如意事十常八九
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我視作真命天女的那一位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個連A Cup都不到的 只有AA Cup的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為參考 哥哥的妻子弘子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是G Cup
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提小町是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡便是築波山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,築波山 歌垣的舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前男女互相詠歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一夜裡互訴愛意的盛名之地 我終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還是那麼熱情高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想來這裡好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因為這可是築波山啊 歌垣的舞臺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就走過了我的任職之地三河
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果來到了這麼東邊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我還有公事就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於只剩我們兩人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在不是做這種事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是絕不能讓小町和業平單獨相處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 難得來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來一場歌垣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼些人來聯誼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣啊 確實還缺少一位女性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊看看找個合適的對象過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆就先隨便逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他太靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易cos了一下僧人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是也能稍微捨棄一下俗念就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 亂來也得有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我現在就該果斷點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小町
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我一…一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你！我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 康秀大人真是的 真會說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說玩笑話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我很看重長相的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也好 我們倆人來玩歌垣遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2100)\c&H9B8D8D&\bord1.3\3c&H000000&\shad0\fs55\pos(448,355)}扮家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要玩的話得先好好想想設定才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後果然得要互贈戀歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來扮演別人家的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康秀大人就扮演愛上別人妻子的可悲男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 那還真是…可悲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你來詠首和歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把作為歌枕的築波山包括進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,築波…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 完全不懂什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接下一句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G1 大獎賽 in平安京
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生 你預測誰是冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想說是業平 但是我想冒險支持一下哥哥行平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生預測的是行平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望喜撰法師奪冠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你支持哪一位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的信號亮起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 現在是「定家之屋」時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的客人是被稱作良少將的傑出人物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧正遍昭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遍昭先生自從仁明天皇駕崩之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為表忠義毅然出家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄了良岑宗貞這一俗名 改名遍昭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定家大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不叫我遍昭 而叫我宗貞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 不過為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為世間一提到遍昭 就會想到花和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…和尚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 話說僧正遍昭是不是很好色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 他還說什麼少女的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全都沒有斬斷塵緣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是花和尚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}花和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你在《百人一首》中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這首和歌後面以遍昭署名了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你出家後潛心修行 登上僧正之高位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是表達對此的敬意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好幾個名字的人的確很難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像貞信公和謙德公他們也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性中我還有很多不知道她們本名的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就取了她們的別稱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清少納言 紫式部 小野小町大人就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如右大將道綱的母親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就像是「道綱君媽媽」一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說吉子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉子家只有女兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我最喜歡和宗貞大人一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡只能玩人偶娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宗貞大人能在外面一起玩好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我也像有個小妹妹一樣 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能把宗貞大人 喚作哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那以後 我和吉子便如兄妹一般長大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒有發展成戀情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉子叫我哥哥 我也覺得那樣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你也快從「哥哥」畢業了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為百夜訪達成之後就要結婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互以名字相稱才是常理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗貞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗貞先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是兄妹相稱最好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有點悖德的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜將為您贈上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一夜的美夢 每一夜的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到牛郎俱樂部 Heian
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是店長 在原行平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上將為您介紹本店的當家帥氣牛郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店No.5 年下系文學青年牛郎 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技是撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請多多傳授與我啊 姐姐大人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店No.4 才藝系牛郎 康秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿手技藝是冷笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牛郎店長舒一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店No.3 自大系傲嬌牛郎 貞明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被他罵的女性急速增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼 還不快點過來 母豬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 再多罵點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店No.2 清爽的哥哥牛郎 宗貞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無微不至的照料 百夜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否允許我到你的閨房造訪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是 本店No.1牛郎 業平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為您獻上 甜蜜的愛語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 請收下我滿腔的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此可愛 真想在夢中也能互訴衷腸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真好啊 業平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀高子 等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的唐紅色盛裝也是如此相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐培里儂開10瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.51,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ひさかたの\N夜中斟酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.35,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ひかるさかずき よもすがら \N沐光似永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.77,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}どんどんぴんく \N漸染粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.19,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ぺりぺりしゃんしゃん\N乒乓碰杯聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.90,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}どんどんぴんく \N漸染粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:34.94,hg3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ぺりぺりしゃんしゃん\N乒乓碰杯聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到唐培里儂的點單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛郎俱樂部 Heian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯集著多彩的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著您的光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G1 大獎賽 in平安京
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是主持人 藤原定家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是助手 宇都宮賴綱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的嘉賓是對夫妻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是新婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 不知道會聽到怎樣的情話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我們請出這對夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夫妻 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽成院貞明 和綏子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說兩位是從小就認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是從那個時候就開始注意到對方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想起來 說不定就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 丟人的青蛙女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剛才這句是「我愛你哦親愛的」的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說 你個母豬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你做成火鍋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才這句是「可愛得讓人想一口吃掉」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 醜女 再說話就讓你在池子裡吊一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才這句是「今晚不放你走」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎樣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家就立刻…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話 想我撕爛你的嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G1 大獎賽 in平安京
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是負責實況播音的定家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽進入中間階段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位選手似乎都開始了檢修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場的賴綱先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這裡是清水寺 我是賴綱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 各位選手的隊伍都在緊張準備中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗貞大人 車輪檢修完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,業平大人 請喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心也吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 業平那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小一個中將也敢跑到我前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 綏子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 貞明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿酒來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給牛喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給牠下點興奮劑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢修站亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「定家之屋」的最後一位嘉賓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平安中期的名歌人 藤原公任先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會被叫來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的嘉賓都是出場過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次出場是來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來故事要進入平安中期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為代表那個時期的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們邀請了公任前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 當時的太政大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原道長 不是更能勝任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽 聽說公任前輩當時曾向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「藤式部」的紫式部女士的會盟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出過援手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與《枕草子》的作者清少納言女士也有過交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才覺得 公任前輩作為那個時代的文學界人士的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來參加節目是最合適不過的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫做領袖實在是很自大 我不是很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 差不多就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我精通和歌 漢詩 管弦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許被稱作領袖也沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}太好了 心情稍微變好了點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選出來的百人一首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選和歌的標准是不是有點鬆懈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我 家持的かささぎの就不會選進去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被後世稱為「後中書王」的具平親王居然沒入選
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 一百首和歌裡有四十三首戀歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平衡感太差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是受親戚所托才選的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在出家人的家裡掛滿戀歌什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想秀一下愛好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這看不起人的態度算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢打我堂堂大納言公任真是無禮至極
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然事情發展到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用《三十六人撰》打敗你的《百人一首》吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安 歌人卡牌大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定家vs公任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安歌人卡牌大戰是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用設定了能力值的歌人的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行的卡牌對戰類游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命值是30000PT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把對手的生命值降到0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者 對手的牌庫無牌時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰區域分為攻擊區和防守區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被召喚到攻擊區域的歌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一個回合可以攻擊對手的攻擊區歌人或者牌手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被召喚到防御區的歌人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.52,0:17:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能在牌手被攻擊時防御
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 在自己的回合開始時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以消耗100生命值讓一個歌人移動區域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌人的能力值也叫做力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌人們的對戰 力量值高的獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了的歌人會進入墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量相同即為平手 兩方均進入墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚歌人會消耗力量值一半量的生命值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量值高的歌人 召喚的風險也更大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命值會在下一個自己的回合的維持階段回復1000PT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無法超過30000PT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 也存在擁有特殊異能的歌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇怎樣的歌人來組牌 會成為勝利的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回合 公任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚中務到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚文屋康秀到攻擊區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三回合 公任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第四回合 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚春道列樹到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用文屋康秀攻擊牌手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用生命值接受攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不防御？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第五回合 公任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被輕視了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第六回合 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將列樹移動到攻擊區
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚參議篁到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用康秀和列樹攻擊牌手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用生命值接受攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七回合 公任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定家 你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將中務移動到攻擊區
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動異能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命值不足10000時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚萬葉歌人的消耗值變為十分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚山部赤人 大伴家持 柿本人麻呂到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來 是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十六人撰的異能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每召喚一個歌人 力量值加1000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中務的力量值變為10000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊牌手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用篁防御
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第八回合 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防不住就會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將康秀移動到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用僧侶異能將列樹置入墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0消耗召喚喜撰法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用六歌仙異能使雙方各加2000力量值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再召喚業平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量值加2000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,業平因三十六人撰異能 再加4000力量值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 召喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第九回合 公任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加固防御嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我的牌庫裡全是三十六人撰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量值還會再增加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將中務移動到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚源順到防御區 回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第十回合 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來詠歌吧 定家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓牌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公任前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我移動到攻擊區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 召喚式子內親王到防御區
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動異能 定家之葛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以外的所有歌人都無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 你就沒有防御歌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(640,660)}こぬひとを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俟君不復返
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貫之前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能打架哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位都是優秀的歌人 和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定家 你的百人一首實在太優秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再就和歌這個話題聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 貫之前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以要個簽名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G1 大獎賽 決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘈雜撞擊聲不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢修站還是亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賴綱先生 現在的狀況是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有一輛車衝了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宗貞大人的牛車
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度 還完全比不上百夜之行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉子 讓我把勝利獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離混亂的良岑宗貞
